      "updated_at": "2026-03-21T03:27:11Z",
      "body": "If phone verification is blocking you: submit your Claude account email via [this form](https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdaK8KdXLL_BX1GY26NmntfyCq1EUGx_M_lxYnxuFiW0tgy4w/viewform). We're processing submissions continuously — most go through within a day, though it can take a little longer. Try signing in again the next day, and once more after that if needed.\n\nAll submissions received so far have been processed. If you've waited a couple days and still can't get in, it's most likely an email mismatch: you should have gotten a Google Forms confirmation email at the address you entered, and if that never arrived it was probably a typo. Resubmit with the exact email you use to log into Claude.\n\nThanks for your patience while we work on a permanent fix.",
